The different types of engines used in trucks and buses include diesel engines, gasoline engines, and natural gas engines.

5. What are the current trends in the truck and bus engines market?
Some current trends in the truck and bus engines market include the increasing adoption of electric and hybrid engines, and the development of more fuel-efficient and environmentally friendly engines.

